                <h3> How to get started with angel investing? </h3>
                  <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                      
                      <div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element ">
                          <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                              <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Australia has now passed the legislative framework allowing retail investors – that’s you – to participate in a new Crowd-Sourced Funding (CSF) regime just like the US, Europe, Asia and New Zealand. This type of investing structure may also be called </span><a href="https://www.venturecrowd.com.au/s/syndicate-investing"><span style="font-weight: 400;">syndicate investing</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Anyone residing in Australia and who is at least 18 years old can now invest in CSF offers made by an investment property company like VentureCrowd. We have already successfully raised </span><a href="https://www.venturecrowd.com.au/s/venture-capital"><span style="font-weight: 400;">venture capital</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> for over 4 years from wholesale investors with over $140m raised across 100 successful deals.&nbsp;</span></p>
                              
                          </div>
